'''馬庫斯·貝蒂內利'''（{{lang-en|Marcus Bettinelli}}；{{bd|1992年|5月24日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的主要位置是守門員，但也可以勝任中後衛。現效力於[[英超|英超]]球隊[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切爾西]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/january/10/new-deal-for-marcus|title=New Deal For Marcus|publisher=Fulham FC|date=10 January 2014|accessdate=10 January 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110125210/http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/january/10/new-deal-for-marcus|archivedate=2014-01-10}}</ref>。他也是英格蘭U21國家隊的一員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/under-21/2014/nov/squad-named-for-portugal-france-061114|title=England Under-21s squad named for double header|work=thefa.com|date=6 November 2014|accessdate=28 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/mar/27/czech-republic-england-under-21s-friendly-match-report|title=Tom Carroll scores winner for England Under-21s against Czech Republic|work=The Guardian|date=27 March 2015|accessdate=28 March 2015}}</ref>。曾經代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]參加比賽。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/45413352 |title=England call up Marcus Bettinelli as Adam Lallana withdraws |website=BBC Sport |accessdate=4 September 2018 |date=4 September 2018}}</ref>

